data.name: mobile_active_vms_windows
data.query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS count FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND live_duration_secs IS MISSING AND os like '%win%' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000,'day') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(), 'day')

data.name: mobile_active_vms_linux
data.query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS count FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND live_duration_secs IS MISSING AND os not like '%win%' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000,'day') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(), 'day')

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_daily
data.query: SELECT MAX(created_time*1000) as timestamp, (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'day') order by timestamp asc

data.name: mobile_vms_created_daily
data.query: SELECT MAX(created_time*1000) as timestamp, count(*) AS count FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'day') order by timestamp asc

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_weekly
data.query: SELECT (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours, MAX(created_time)*1000 AS timestamp FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_PART_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'iso_week') ORDER BY timestamp ASC

data.name: mobile_vms_created_weekly
data.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as count, MAX(created_time)*1000 AS timestamp FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_PART_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'iso_week') AS week ORDER BY timestamp ASC

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_monthly
data.query: SELECT MAX(created_time*1000) as timestamp, (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'month') order by timestamp asc

data.name: mobile_vms_created_monthly
data.query: SELECT MAX(created_time*1000) as timestamp, count(*) AS count FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'month') order by timestamp asc

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_today
data.query: SELECT NVL((SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600, 0) AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'day') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'day')

data.name: mobile_vms_created_today
data.query: SELECT count(*) AS vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'day') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'day')

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_this_week
data.query: SELECT NVL((SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600, 0) AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_PART_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'iso_week') = DATE_PART_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'iso_week') AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'year') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(), 'year')

data.name: mobile_vms_created_this_week
data.query: SELECT COUNT(*) AS vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_PART_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'iso_week') = DATE_PART_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'iso_week') AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'year') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(), 'year')

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_this_month
data.query: SELECT NVL((SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600, 0) AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'month') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'month')

data.name: mobile_vms_created_this_month
data.query: SELECT count(*) AS vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' AND DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'month') = DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(CLOCK_MILLIS(),'month')

data.name: mobile_daily_stats
data.query: select timestamp, (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours, count(*) as vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'day') as timestamp order by timestamp desc

data.name: mobile_weekly_stats
data.query: SELECT MAX(created_time*1000) as timestamp, (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours, count(*) as vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_PART_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'iso_week') order by timestamp desc

data.name: mobile_monthly_stats
data.query: select timestamp, (SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours, count(*) as vms_created FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000, 'month') as timestamp order by timestamp desc

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_by_os
data.query: SELECT os,timestamp,(SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY os, DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000,'day') AS timestamp ORDER BY timestamp ASC

data.name: mobile_compute_hours_by_xen_host
data.query: SELECT origin,timestamp,(SUM(NVL(live_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(create_duration_secs,0))+SUM(NVL(delete_duration_secs,0)))/3600 AS compute_hours FROM `QE-dynserver-pool` WHERE ipaddr != '' GROUP BY origin, DATE_TRUNC_MILLIS(created_time*1000,'day') AS timestamp ORDER BY timestamp ASC
